{"tid":1186142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高質] 建設民主钟国","createTime":"2019-06-04T17:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T17:11:02.000Z","uid":132739,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"139026473552e796ef01f409a0180f64e3a854bd","tid":1186142,"uid":132739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q8KTU_8acKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq8KTU_8acKs&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=50d57a0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q8KTU_8acKs</a><br />\n比你身邊唔知6月9號上唔上嚟嘅人睇啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e9de8acef74175c64f06ec4e7a327860907934","tid":1186142,"uid":244332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6/9，香港人，銅鑼灣見"},{"pid":"74bdddb48c1015a17fbfa83e803eb89189cf22e5","tid":1186142,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:52:47.000Z","msg":"光豬= 香港？"},{"pid":"0982ee993192435c67f707e62fb4940f7fff06d7","tid":1186142,"uid":132739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74bdddb48c1015a17fbfa83e803eb89189cf22e5","tid":1186142,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:52:47.000Z","msg":"光豬= 香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"角色圖： <br />\n哈哈：參與集會嘅香港市民（因得罪中國而被引渡) <br />\n石鎮：廢老（一向以為共產黨係好人） <br />\n光洙：一直置身事外嘅人（強調我唔搞政治政治唔會搞我） <br />\n在石：商家（以為係共產黨統治下抽油水，結果共產黨打到嚟全部財產被沒收) <br />\n智孝and Gary：遲咗醒覺嘅人（發現一切都太遲然後其中一方變節)"},{"pid":"3cd28cd33190e35625d6e02b3e4bd6b0a8aa48c2","tid":1186142,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事關香港歷史之重大變局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想借大家少少位用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOPvJL6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOPvJL6.png&h=344452d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止惡法！為時未晚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留意返由於預計示威人數好多，民陣已經將起點改咗喺維園！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n<br />\n集合地點：<span style=\"color: red;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百國聯軍助陣！感謝海外港人為香港人嘅未來而作出嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG0SmhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG0SmhW.png&h=5d5fe630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>愛因斯坦 (Albert Einstein)：「The world will not be destoryed by those who do evil, but by these who watch them without doing anything.(這個世界不會被那些作惡多端的人毀滅，而是冷眼旁觀、選擇保持緘默的人)」；鄭有傑(導演):「良心的沉默是邪惡的幫兇。」<br />\n<br />\n好多時歷史中嘅轉折位都係由表面上微不足道嘅小事/小人物而形成嘅，所以我地更加唔可以睇小自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=d764195b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=220bd579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"e905bb844080d2491bf0195f89299eeaf43cfaef","tid":1186142,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}